             <div class="et_pb_text_inner">
              <h2>
               Society for Social Neuroscience
              </h2>
              <p>
               Founded by John T. Cacioppo in 2009, The
               <a href="http://s4sn.org/drupal/">
                Society for Social Neuroscience
               </a>
               is an international, interdisciplinary, scientific, nonprofit society established to advance and foster scientific research, training, and applications. [
               <a href="http://s4sn.org/drupal/">
                More…
               </a>
               ]
              </p>
             </div>
            </div>
